ing: 1 (15 ounce) can chickpeas, drained and rinsed

des: "Chopped zucchini, chickpeas, tomatoes, and fresh basil in a light balsamic dressing. Or you can use red wine vinegar!  Makes a great side dish or light lunch. Not necessary, but best if chilled at least a couple hours to let flavors blend."
ins: Mix zucchini, chickpeas, tomatoes, red bell pepper, onion, feta, Kalamata olives, olive oil, basil, vinegar, rosemary, capers, garlic, oregano, red pepper flakes, salt, and black pepper together in a large bowl.
